channel.title: - Wisdomrsps *OSRS* - BETA
channel.description:
WisdomRsps is a brand new osrs server based on the awesome Vencillio source.
We are constantly updating and are open as beta (No reset after Beta)
We have many features such as an npc to check drop tables, cool titles, awesome donator zone and so much more!!!
What are you waiting for? come join us for an unforgettable rsps experience.
----> [url=http://www.wisdomrsps.com]www.wisdomrsps.com[/url] <----
[center]Features:
Bosses
King black dragon Sea troll queen Barrelchest Corporal beast Daggonoths kings Godwars Zulrah Kraken Callisto Scorpia AND MANY MORE!
minigames
Barrows Warriors Guild Duel Arena Pest Control Fight Caves Weapon Game Clan Wars
I do not own this server!
PICTURES WILL BE ADDED SOON ASAP
www.wisdomrsps.com [/center]
